summary: An ordinance amending the title and section 1 of Ordinance No. 29253, entitled: "An ordinance accepting a deed from King County a county of and within the State of Washington; to the City of Seattle, dated the \_\_ day of \_\_\_ 1912, to a certain tract of land situated in the City of Seattle, King County, and described as follows to-wit: the east 9 feet of lot 4, Block 3, Charles Addition to the City of Seattle; appropriating $21.98 from the general fund of the City of Seattle in payment therefor, and declaring an emergency.
